<div class="container">
  <div class="row hiring_result">
    <div class="col-md-10 col-md-offset-1">
      <div class="hiring_result_head">
        <h2 class="text">Your Results</h2>
        <p>Thank you for taking our assessment. This gives us a sense of who you are and serves as a tool for you to evaluate if strategy consulting and working in a remote environment is right for you.</p>
      </div>
      <% if @remoteScore >= 14 && @strategyScore >= 16 %>
        <div class="response-box">
          <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">Summary</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body" >
                <h2>Your Scores:</h2>
                <h5>Remote Score: <%= @remoteScore %> </h5>
                <h5>Strategy Score: <%= @remoteScore %> </h5>
                <p>
                  We think you're going to love working remotely! You seem to have all the right qualities it takes to work in a remote environment and enjoy our line of work. We encourage you to take the next step by completing our application.
                </p>
                <a href="http://www.artemisconnection.com/application" class="btn btn-default btn-apply btn-lg" style="margin-left:10px">Apply</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% elsif @remoteScore >= 10 && @strategyScore >= 14 %>
        <div class="response-box">
          <div class="panel panel-default">
              <div class="panel-heading">
                <h4 class="panel-title">Summary</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="panel-body" >
                <h2>Your Scores:</h2>
                <h5>Remote Score: <%= @remoteScore %> </h5>
                <h5>Strategy Score: <%= @remoteScore %> </h5>
                <p>
                  We think you would be a strong remote worker but don't quite have the collaborator experience. Since you are so close to being a good fit, why not apply and we will see if we can work with you.
                </p>
                <a href="http://www.artemisconnection.com/application" class="btn btn-default btn-apply btn-lg">Apply</a>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      <% elsif @remoteScore < 10 || @strategyScore < 12 %>
      <div class="response-box">
        <div class="panel panel-default">
            <div class="panel-heading">
              <h4 class="panel-title">Summary</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="panel-body" >
              <p style="color: red">Strategy and remote work is not for everyone. We find people that gravitate towards it enjoy problem solving, are open to learning new technologies, self-motivated and are comfortable not working in a social environment.
                </p>
                <hr>
              <p style="margin-bottom: 0.8em; margin-top: 0.8em; color: #000; font-weight: bold;">We wish you best in your search and recommend you check out the following companies:</p>
              <h4>Ex-Consultants Agency: <a href="https://www.exconsultantsagency.com/">https://www.exconsultantsagency.com/</a></h4>
              <h4>SpareHire: <a href="http://www.sparehire.com">sparehire.com</a></h4>
              <h4>Hillgate: <a href="https://www.hillgateconnect.com/">https://www.hillgateconnect.com/</a></h4>
              <h4>AngelList: <a href="https://angel.co/">https://angel.co/</a></h4>
              <h4>Catalant: <a href="https://gocatalant.com/">https://gocatalant.com/</a></h4>
              <h4>Remote.co: <a href="https://remote.co/">https://remote.co/</a></h4>
              <h4>Flexjobs: <a href="https://www.flexjobs.com/">https://www.flexjobs.com/</a></h4>
              <h4>Talent Response: <a href="http://www.talentresponse.com/">http://www.talentresponse.com/</a></h4>
              <h4>Join our Jobs + Gigs Facebook Group to get learn about opportunities: <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/363826397390143/?ref=pages_profile_groups_tab&source_id=1540317379603299">Jobs + Gigs Facebook Group</a></h4>
              <h4>Business Talent Group: <a href="https://businesstalentgroup.com">https://businesstalentgroup.com</a></h4>
              <a href="http://www.artemisconnection.com/" class="btn btn-default btn-apply btn-lg">Back To Home</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
